MobileProductQuestionContext is a Form
    title is "ProductQuestion"
    Layout
        display as text
            single column
                RecallNotice
                RecallNotice.Name
                RecallProduct.ProductName
                RecallProduct.ProductDescription
                    label is "Description"
            visible when (HasLocationActivity)
                single column
                    RecallProduct.RecallTaskInstruction
                    RecallProduct.TaskInstructionDescription
